openruyi-local
================

openruyi-local is the vendor-owned base authselect profile for openRuyi.

It is intentionally local-first, systemd-aware, and minimal:
- local UNIX accounts remain the default identity source
- nss-systemd is enabled for systemd-managed dynamic users
- PAM policy lives in authselect-managed system-auth/password-auth/postlogin files

Service-specific PAM entry points are expected to stay thin and defer shared
policy to this profile.
